The concept of what neutral supporters "generally considered" entertaining is a subjective measure that is not recorded in this database.

Even if we tried to use total goals as a proxy for entertainment, Piast Gliwice ranks 14th out of 16 teams in average total goals per home match (2.4 goals/match) in the 2015/2016 Poland Ekstraklasa season, which would contradict rather than support the claim.
